metadata.name: Cthultoven
metadata.description:
"Something strange is happening... I don't feel the music like I used to. Tentacles are born from my head, the piano is moving, violins come out of the walls... I think I should create more music but I just can't. Music has created me and this monster that is born from my inside."

If you buy this artwork you will receive a SPECIAL SECRET GIFT related to the piece.

Technical details:
 - Size: 4064 x 4730
 - Video lenght: 1:25 min

Please contact mrhereman@gmail.com with proof of ownership and I will send you the high res video, all the frames animation and a SPECIAL SECRET GIFT related with the piece.
